This are the gentoo ebuids for building valama:
valadoc-9999.ebuild
valama-9999.ebuild

Copy the content of the gentoo directory in your local portage overlay.
Each time you issue each "emerge -v valama" the acual git repository git://github.com/Valama/valama.git
is downloaded, compiled and istalled.

The valadoc-9999.ebuild is a slightly modified version of:
http://code.google.com/p/vala-overlay/source/browse/dev-util/valadoc/valadoc-9999.ebuild
